{"tid":415512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"家中放觀音像被質疑　基督徒何君堯：有什麼問題？我是中國人","createTime":"2017-09-27T04:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T06:29:53.000Z","uid":136994,"like":7,"dislike":185,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"49e46dc2b49a11a85549edd9c3b74c3224d280d1","tid":415512,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:42:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170927/s00001/1506477440372\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170927%2Fs00001%2F1506477440372&d=n7Fcs58SPlRIObL34jjjWviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=9aed2f73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170927%2Fs00001%2F1506477440372&h=e96ab451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170927/s00001/1506477440372</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170927/s00001/8bbe038bea519b73962dd5b29de5acbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170927%2Fs00001%2F8bbe038bea519b73962dd5b29de5acbf.jpg&h=c0a70eaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n立法會議員何君堯幾乎每天晚上都會在家中進行facebook直播，發表對社會議題看法之餘，亦回應網民提問。近日有網民發現，自稱基督徒的何君堯家中擺放了一尊觀音像，因而質疑他是否真正基督徒，何君堯昨晚於fb直播中回應事件，反問「有什麼問題呢？」<br />\n<br />\n何君堯在直播中指出，該觀音像是其母購入及擺放，「我覺得幾好啊（觀音像放家中），我對中國&hellip;&hellip;我是中國人來的嘛」，又反問「所有（東西）都是擺設，有什麼問題呢？」<br />\n<br />\n至於基督徒家中放觀音像是否恰當，何君堯只說「人言可畏，我們是清者自清，謠言止於智者」。他之後取來一樽酒，稱「難道有酒放在這裏，又是供奉酒仙？」<br />\n<br />\n他強調，「這些網上欺凌、中傷人說話不要得」，預告未來要搞「反對網上欺凌運動」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我宜家先知道原來基督徒所講嘅「唯一的神」嘅係觀音，唔係耶和華！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真正的基督徒唔知有啲咩想同何君堯講呢？<br />\n我唔係基督徒都先贈你一句：死後落地獄啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong>"},{"pid":"eaa340d70fe154fae1e445b81b6064ba13f91199","tid":415512,"uid":33730,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:44:46.000Z","msg":"支國人? 支共一向無神論架<br />\n真係好撚柒蠢, 投票俾佢班人真係白痴都不如"},{"pid":"1eefc8a9c343fe7dec5727b8fcc62b7648362741","tid":415512,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:45:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36ddea53f6f15c74bd1c95daa49b8a7677af6359","tid":415512,"uid":121580,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:47:02.000Z","msg":"睇聖經la屌,拜其他偶像落地獄呀"},{"pid":"bea8b14eb22f985fce807c9ffdd36243d78d9cd5","tid":415512,"uid":35790,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:47:06.000Z","msg":"觀世音係古印度人<br />\n唔係支那人"},{"pid":"a3bc9f9bbf4fd4680e862fe537690ee1f4d0bbd9","tid":415512,"uid":121580,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:49:53.000Z","msg":"聖經有講如果家中其他人信其他神要點做嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd606e97ff44aaae16928c99b1da1896d1e644f","tid":415512,"uid":28195,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:50:30.000Z","msg":"越黎越九唔搭八，思緒超級混亂，已經違反《精神健康條例》，不適合做議員"},{"pid":"579cb9176900e8c0f8cf175d0621ee0cec78723e","tid":415512,"uid":14816,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:51:09.000Z","msg":"連基督徒身分都係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb750c01256f17de6e7282c930a6d7c546f04910","tid":415512,"uid":54279,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:51:27.000Z","msg":"不可拜別神，唔係基督徒都知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a94b54203992148de5a0c74b6af4270bfdf86f85","tid":415512,"uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:51:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連基督徒身分都係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" 